    "11. User Responsibilities": "11. User Responsibilities",
    "Users must: (a) Secure their account credentials and private keys; (b) Verify all transaction details before confirmation; (c) Not attempt to manipulate, exploit, or abuse platform features; (d) Comply with applicable laws in their jurisdiction; (e) Not misrepresent the platform as a financial service or investment opportunity to others.": "Users must: (a) Secure their account credentials and private keys; (b) Verify all transaction details before confirmation; (c) Not attempt to manipulate, exploit, or abuse platform features; (d) Comply with applicable laws in their jurisdiction; (e) Not misrepresent the platform as a financial service or investment opportunity to others.",
    "12. Prohibited Activities": "12. Prohibited Activities",
    "Users may NOT: (a) Create multiple accounts or use automated systems; (b) Exploit bugs or vulnerabilities for unfair advantage; (c) Engage in any form of market manipulation; (d) Use the platform for money laundering or illegal activities; (e) Promote the platform as an investment or money-making scheme; (f) Harass other community members.": "Users may NOT: (a) Create multiple accounts or use automated systems; (b) Exploit bugs or vulnerabilities for unfair advantage; (c) Engage in any form of market manipulation; (d) Use the platform for money laundering or illegal activities; (e) Promote the platform as an investment or money-making scheme; (f) Harass other community members.",
    "13. Service Modifications": "13. Service Modifications",
    "AccessDigital reserves the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any platform features, reward mechanisms, or services at any time. This includes adjustments to point distributions, activity requirements, and network parameters. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance of modified terms.": "AccessDigital reserves the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any platform features, reward mechanisms, or services at any time. This includes adjustments to point distributions, activity requirements, and network parameters. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance of modified terms.",
    "14. Limitation of Liability": "14. Limitation of Liability",
    "AccessDigital, its operators, and affiliates shall NOT be liable for: (a) Loss of ACCESS points due to user error, security breaches, or technical issues; (b) Any perceived financial loss related to ACCESS point value; (c) Third-party actions or external market conditions; (d) Service interruptions or data loss; (e) Decisions made based on platform information.": "AccessDigital, its operators, and affiliates shall NOT be liable for: (a) Loss of ACCESS points due to user error, security breaches, or technical issues; (b) Any perceived financial loss related to ACCESS point value; (c) Third-party actions or external market conditions; (d) Service interruptions or data loss; (e) Decisions made based on platform information.",
    "15. Account Termination": "15. Account Termination",
    "We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms, engage in suspicious activity, or pose risks to platform integrity. Upon termination, accumulated ACCESS points may be forfeited. Users may request account deletion through profile settings, resulting in permanent removal of all associated data.": "We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms, engage in suspicious activity, or pose risks to platform integrity. Upon termination, accumulated ACCESS points may be forfeited. Users may request account deletion through profile settings, resulting in permanent removal of all associated data.",
    "16. Intellectual Property": "16. Intellectual Property",
    "All platform content, branding, code, and designs are proprietary to AccessDigital. Users may not copy, modify, or distribute platform materials without explicit written permission. The Access Network protocol and AccessScan explorer are part of our intellectual property portfolio.": "All platform content, branding, code, and designs are proprietary to AccessDigital. Users may not copy, modify, or distribute platform materials without explicit written permission. The Access Network protocol and AccessScan explorer are part of our intellectual property portfolio.",
    "17. Dispute Resolution": "17. Dispute Resolution",
    "Any disputes arising from platform use shall be resolved through good-faith negotiation. Users agree that ACCESS points have no predetermined monetary value for dispute calculation purposes. AccessDigital decisions regarding account status and point balances are final within the platform ecosystem.": "Any disputes arising from platform use shall be resolved through good-faith negotiation. Users agree that ACCESS points have no predetermined monetary value for dispute calculation purposes. AccessDigital decisions regarding account status and point balances are final within the platform ecosystem.",
    "18. Regulatory Compliance": "18. Regulatory Compliance",
    "Users are responsible for understanding and complying with laws applicable in their jurisdiction regarding digital assets and blockchain platforms. AccessDigital does not provide tax, legal, or regulatory advice. Features may be restricted in certain regions based on regulatory requirements.": "Users are responsible for understanding and complying with laws applicable in their jurisdiction regarding digital assets and blockchain platforms. AccessDigital does not provide tax, legal, or regulatory advice. Features may be restricted in certain regions based on regulatory requirements.",
    "19. Updates to Terms": "19. Updates to Terms",
    "These Terms of Service may be updated periodically. Significant changes will be communicated through platform notifications. Continued platform use after updates constitutes acceptance of revised terms. Users are encouraged to review these terms regularly.": "These Terms of Service may be updated periodically. Significant changes will be communicated through platform notifications. Continued platform use after updates constitutes acceptance of revised terms. Users are encouraged to review these terms regularly.",
    "Acceptance Statement": "Acceptance Statement",
    "By creating an account or using AccessDigital, you confirm that you have read, understood, and agree to these Terms of Service. You acknowledge that ACCESS points are community engagement rewards without guaranteed financial value, and you are participating for the platform experience—not for investment purposes.": "By creating an account or using AccessDigital, you confirm that you have read, understood, and agree to these Terms of Service. You acknowledge that ACCESS points are community engagement rewards without guaranteed financial value, and you are participating for the platform experience—not for investment purposes.",
