    // Privacy Policy
    "Privacy Policy & Terms of Service": "隐私政策与服务条款",
"1. Introduction": "1. 介绍",
"Welcome to AccessoireDigital. Before proceeding, please review and accept our Privacy Policy and Terms of Service.": "欢迎使用 AccessoireDigital。在继续之前，请查看并接受我们的隐私政策与服务条款。",
"2. Platform Services": "2. 平台服务",
"AccessoireDigital is a comprehensive digital assets platform offering cloud processing services, digital account management, and secure transaction processing. Users can earn Points through our 24-hour processing cycles and participate in our referral program.": "AccessoireDigital 是一个综合性的数字资产平台，提供云处理服务、数字账户管理和安全交易处理。用户可以通过我们的 24 小时处理周期赚取积分，并参与推荐计划。",

"3. Platform Purpose": "3. 平台目的",
"Access-Network is a digital engagement platform that rewards active participation through a secure distributed point system. Points are earned through daily activities, referrals, and community interaction. These digital assets can be transferred between users and stored in personal wallets for future use within the ecosystem.": "Access-Network 是一个数字互动平台，通过安全的分布式积分系统奖励积极参与。积分可通过日常活动、推荐和社区互动获得。这些数字资产可以在用户之间转移，并存储在个人钱包中，以便在生态系统中未来使用。",

"4. Account & Transaction System": "4. 账户与交易系统",
"Each user receives a unique digital account address for sending and receiving Points. All transactions are recorded on our secure digital network with full transparency and immutable transaction history.": "每位用户都会获得一个独特的数字账户地址，用于发送和接收积分。所有交易都会记录在我们的安全数字网络上，确保完全透明且交易历史不可更改。",

"5. Processing & Rewards System": "5. 处理与奖励系统",
"Users can participate in cloud processing to earn Points every 24 hours. Processing rewards are distributed based on activity and referral bonuses. All earnings are automatically credited to your account balance upon completion of processing cycles.": "用户可以参与云处理，每 24 小时赚取积分。处理奖励根据活动和推荐奖金分配。所有收益将在处理周期完成后自动记入您的账户余额。",

"6. Referral Program": "6. 推荐计划",
"Users can invite others using their unique referral code. Successful referrals earn bonuses for both the referrer and new user. All referral rewards are processed automatically and added to account balances.": "用户可以使用其唯一的推荐码邀请他人。成功推荐可为推荐人和新用户赚取奖金。所有推荐奖励会自动处理并加入账户余额。",

"7. Transaction Fees & Policies": "7. 交易费用与政策",
"All transactions include a minimal network fee of 0.00002 Points to maintain network security. Minimum transaction amounts and daily limits may apply to ensure system stability and security.": "所有交易均包含 0.00002 积分的最低网络费用，以维护网络安全。为确保系统稳定和安全，可能适用最低交易金额和每日限额。",

"8. Data Collection & Security": "8. 数据收集与安全",
"We collect essential information including your Google account details (name, email, profile picture) for authentication purposes only. YOUR DATA IS COMPLETELY PRIVATE: We do NOT share, sell, or distribute your personal information to any third parties under any circumstances. All user data and private keys are encrypted using industry-standard AES-256 security protocols and stored securely in our protected databases. Your information is used exclusively for platform functionality and your account security.": "我们仅收集基本信息，包括您的 Google 帐户详情（姓名、电子邮件、头像），仅用于身份验证。您的数据完全私密：在任何情况下，我们都不会向第三方共享、出售或分发您的个人信息。所有用户数据和私钥均采用行业标准 AES-256 安全协议加密，并安全存储在我们的受保护数据库中。您的信息仅用于平台功能和账户安全。",

"9. Privacy & Data Usage": "9. 隐私与数据使用",
"Your personal information is used solely for platform functionality, security, and user experience enhancement. We do not share your data with third parties without explicit consent, except as required by applicable laws.": "您的个人信息仅用于平台功能、安全和用户体验的提升。未经明确同意，我们不会与第三方共享您的数据，但法律要求除外。",

"10. User Responsibilities": "10. 用户责任",
"Users are responsible for securing their account credentials and private keys. AccessoireDigital is not liable for losses due to user negligence, unauthorized access, or failure to follow security guidelines.": "用户有责任保护其账户凭证和私钥。因用户疏忽、未经授权的访问或未遵循安全指南造成的损失，AccessoireDigital 不承担责任。",

"11. Account Deletion & Data Removal": "11. 帐号删除与数据移除",
"Users have the right to permanently delete their account at any time through the profile settings. When you delete your account: (1) All personal data including email, name, and profile information will be permanently removed. (2) All your Points balance will be lost forever and cannot be recovered. (3) Your referral code and all referral relationships will be permanently deleted. (4) All transaction history and activity records will be completely erased. (5) Your wallet and private keys will be permanently deleted. (6) This action is IRREVERSIBLE and CANNOT be undone. Once your account is deleted, there is no way to restore your data, Points, or any information associated with your account. We do not retain any backup copies of deleted accounts.": "用户有权随时通过个人资料设置永久删除其账户。删除账户时：(1) 所有个人数据，包括电子邮件、姓名和个人资料信息，将被永久删除。(2) 您的所有积分余额将永久丢失，无法恢复。(3) 您的推荐码及所有推荐关系将被永久删除。(4) 所有交易历史和活动记录将被完全清除。(5) 您的钱包和私钥将被永久删除。(6) 此操作不可撤销，无法恢复。账户一旦删除，无法恢复任何数据、积分或与账户相关的任何信息。我们不保留已删除账户的任何备份副本。",

"12. Platform Modifications": "12. 平台修改",
"We reserve the right to modify platform features, terms, or policies with reasonable notice to users. Continued use of the platform constitutes acceptance of any updates to these terms.": "我们保留在合理通知用户的情况下修改平台功能、条款或政策的权利。继续使用平台即表示接受这些条款的任何更新。",

